ygData.msgSnippet: Do Dirvish Camps in North Ro until 14th, then go to Oasis and kill caimens and crocs to 18th. From there head to lake rathe until 24th. After that Cazic,
ygData.messageBody:
Do Dirvish Camps in North Ro until 14th, then go to Oasis and kill caimens
and crocs to 18th. From there head to lake rathe until 24th. After that
Cazic, unrest, mistmoor, najema, runnyeye or guk is good.
